"v.擦掉，抹去 【英】 v. 擦掉，抹去(wipe out;erase) 【考】 反义词：blazon(画纹 章); etch(蚀刻) 【记】 ef+face(脸, 表面)→去掉表面→擦 掉 【例】 It is not possible to efface the memory of a loved one. v. 擦掉 = erase; 冲淡(记忆); 隐居 【记】ef去掉, face脸, 表面－去掉表面－擦掉 【类】alliterate: remove = blazon: efface押头韵的诗句不能移动 = 纹章装饰不能擦除 【反】blazon(vt 装饰n 纹章); etch(v 蚀刻); emboss(vt 饰以浮饰)bring to preeminent(使卓越); aggrandize(vt 增加; 夸大)institute(n 学会vt 创立; 开始) 【记】ef (ex 去掉) + face 表面，脸， 从表面去掉，从脸上抹去 【相关】surface 表面 efface (v.)  late 15c., from Middle French effacer, from Old French esfacier (12c.) ""to wipe out, destroy,"" literally ""to remove the face,"" from es- ""out"" (see ex-) + face ""appearance,"" from Latin facies ""face"" (see face (n.)). Related: Effaced; effacing. Compare deface."
